# Invite link module

Read **docs/contracts/module-invite-link.md** before changing share URLs or deep link routing.

## Required patterns

1. All game share URLs/messages → `src/services/inviteLinkService.ts` only.
2. Host share → `shareGameInvite(activity, { asHost: true })` (auto-join when spots open).
3. Public share → `shareGameInvite(activity, { asHost: false })` (game card → request).
4. Rally share → `shareRallyGroupInvite(group)` — do not inline `rallyapp://group-invite` strings.
5. Deep link parsing changes → update `parseAppDeepLink` **and** `__tests__/deepLinking.test.ts`.

Run `npm test -- deepLinking` after link shape changes.
